      "review_summary": "The PR requires admin authentication for explicit brokered AWS Mac host pinning, filters non-admin portal Dedicated Host visibility to hosts attached to visible active macOS leases, and updates related tests and docs.\n\nReproducibility: yes. from source: on the PR head, non-admin host visibility is computed from portalLeases(request), and that path is paginated before the new host filter sees it. A visible active macOS lease outside the first 100 portal leases can therefore lose host detail/VNC authorization.",
